data.description: This is your opportunity to take advantage of a home nestled in the sought-after Huntington Hills Golf and Country Club. A captivated curb appeal with a charming sense of pride takes you to a must have three bedrooms, two bathrooms property with a two-car garage. It has a modern open floor plan and sliding glass door that opens to an enclosed sitting area that permits you to enjoy the immaculate kept subdivision common area. Add to everything a low maintenance living with recently installed solar panels. Be the envy of your neighbors when they receive their electricity bills. New roof was installed on 2020. The Subdivision has a sparkling community swimming pool and a tennis court. The Golf course has a beautiful Club House. Not only you could enjoy the surroundings but also launch your boat in Lake Lester. Conveniently located in the vibrant Lakeland area between Orlando and Tampa give you the ability to enjoy nearby renowned restaurants and attractions. Florida Living at the tips of your hands.  Call to make an appointment to preview this unique gem.
